AMBIENT AUDIO SYSTEM PLACEHOLDER

This directory requires 11 MP3 audio files for the ambient soundscape system.
Each file should be a 30-60 second seamless loop at MP3 format (128-192 kbps).

Required files:
1. temple-drone.mp3 - Default ambient pad (deep resonant drone)
2. scholarly-hum.mp3 - Akademia section (intellectual, library-inspired)
3. paper-rustle.mp3 - Bibliotheke section (tactile paper sounds)
4. hearth-crackle.mp3 - Oikos section (warm fireplace ambience)
5. gallery-echo.mp3 - Pinakotheke section (spacious gallery reverb)
6. concert-hall.mp3 - Odeion section (grand concert hall ambience)
7. stage-ambience.mp3 - Theatron section (theatrical dramatic space)
8. crowd-murmur.mp3 - Agora section (marketplace crowd)
9. conversation.mp3 - Symposion section (conversational ambience)
10. machine-hum.mp3 - Ergasterion section (workshop machinery)
11. clock-tick.mp3 - Khronos section (temporal/clock ambience)

See README.md in this directory for:
- Detailed specifications for each file
- Technical requirements (format, duration, looping, volume)
- Sourcing guidelines (recording, royalty-free libraries, synthesis)
- Integration details with the audio system
- Testing checklist before deployment

These files are referenced in js/config.js and loaded by js/audioLoader.js.
